# Login credentials for automatic cookie generation
#
# Format: loginPageUrl::username::password
# One entry per line. Lines starting with # are comments.
#
# WARNING: This file contains passwords. NEVER commit the real logins.txt to git.
#          Only commit this example file (logins.txt.example).
#
# Usage:
#   1. Copy this file to logins.txt:   cp logins.txt.example logins.txt
#   2. Edit logins.txt with your real credentials
#   3. Run: videodl generate-cookies
#
# Example:
# https://site-ma.example.com/login::myusername::mypassword123
# https://members.example.com/login::user@email.com::SecurePass!
